means "sneery".

36:06.598 --> 36:08.165
"Sneery" like... effectively.

36:08.233 --> 36:09.666
So, like... so, like...

36:09.734 --> 36:11.134
So, you would sneer.

36:11.202 --> 36:12.335
Sneery?

36:12.337 --> 36:13.636
That's my resting face.

36:13.705 --> 36:15.805
Sneery mcbride. Right.

36:18.042 --> 36:20.122
So, that was... it all makes
so much sense right now.

36:21.713 --> 36:25.248
