for the campbells in 1851.-

36:25.250 --> 36:26.816
Robert. Isabella. James.

36:26.818 --> 36:28.151
Margaret. Alexander.

36:28.153 --> 36:30.253
That's my
great-great-grandfather.

36:30.321 --> 36:32.855
But alexander campbell
is listed as a quarrier,

36:32.924 --> 36:34.157
So he would've had a quarry.

36:34.225 --> 36:37.927
He had one? He had a quarry.

36:37.930 --> 36:41.097
They turn up in a couple of post
office directories, as well.

36:41.165 --> 36:42.565
There he is listed.

36:42.634 --> 36:44.200
Wow. Innkeeper?

36:44.203 --> 36:45.568
Innkeeper.

36:45.571 --> 36:47.571
Now, I've got
a slightly later one here,

36:47.639 --> 36:49.839
But by this point,
he's changed his profession.

36:49.841 --> 36:52.209
Alexander... contractor.

36:52.277 --> 36:53.576
He sounds a little shady.

36:53.579 --> 36:56.846
He's jack of
a great number of trades,

36:56.914 --> 37:02.218
