he kind of never quite achieves.

37:02.221 --> 37:04.921
A kind of prominence in the city
that other people do,

37:04.990 --> 37:07.123
And I'm... I have
a sneaking suspicion that.

37:07.191 --> 37:08.891
That's actually on purpose.

37:11.196 --> 37:14.764
At this point in July 1859,

37:14.832 --> 37:17.601
Alexander campbell
purchases two shares.

37:17.669 --> 37:19.936
Previously, we have
detailed records.

37:20.005 --> 37:21.871
Of what cargoes
people were bringing in.

37:21.940 --> 37:24.674
Contraband rum, or...
So, that might...

37:24.743 --> 37:26.542
What... it might be, like, rum.

37:26.545 --> 37:28.378
It could be.
He could be a rumrunner.

